# The Rollercoaster

Simulates rolling terrain with constantly changing power demands. No two hills are the same — some are punchy, others are grinding, and you never quite fully recover. Welcome to the Ardennes.

- 5:00 45%
  - :30 Warm up on the flats
  - 3:00 The road starts rolling in 2 minutes
  - :30 Get ready to shift — a lot
- 10x
  - 1:00 55%..85%
  - 1:00 85%..55%
  - :30 45%
- 3:00 50%
  - :10 Flat section — catch your breath while you can
  - 1:30 Bigger rollers coming up, these ones bite
- 5x
  - 2:00 60%..100%
  - 1:00 100%..60%
  - 1:00 45%
- 3:00 50%
  - :10 One more set of rollers — the sharp ones
  - 1:30 These are short and punchy, stay on it
- 8x
  - :30 50%..110%
  - :30 110%..50%
  - :30 45%
- 5:00 40%
  - :10 That's the last of the hills — coast home
  - 3:00 Spin it out easy, the road is flat from here
